Katakan sahaja ia ditemui. Jadi apa?

00:36:33.760 --> 00:36:35.760
Bagaimanapun, anda perlu berurusan dengannya.

00:36:35.840 --> 00:36:38.280
Dia menyakiti Mek!

00:36:39.640 --> 00:36:40.480
Okay.

00:36:40.560 --> 00:36:43.360
Jadi, jika dia meminta maaf, itu sahaja?

00:36:46.080 --> 00:36:47.800
Tawan, cuma minta maaf.

00:36:49.240 --> 00:36:52.200
Ayah... saya tak buat salah pun.

